encodeLine(ArrayList<String>, ErrorOut, SymbolTable, ErrorTable, InstructTable, DirectiveTable, int, int, IntermediateFile, String) - Method in interface EncoderInterface
encodeLine takes input from the parser and encodes into binary the current
line we are on; in the case of symbols, they are represented as [symbolname]
and are evaluated in the object file creation.
